g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過諗起支那豬比人秒咗嘅嬲豬樣就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n727，愛與和平淨化元朗<br />\n728，追究警察嗜血瀆職"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:37:36.000Z","msg":"歐盟認清中國<br />\n對我地係大利好"},{"pid":"8e82d1b19a3f4a58db84520fe72f9201f98cd1c9","tid":1357784,"uid":14433,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:48:25.000Z","msg":"要比全世界知道，支那根本就係地球癌細胞，不切不快"},{"pid":"a4710ff10dde43f83b72aaf75c75b0e671f51952","tid":1357784,"uid":247903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:01:40.000Z","msg":"中國人唔係最鐘意話人唔握手係冇禮貌咩！<br />\n而家歧視德國人呀！"},{"pid":"95bba58916a64d9d67264087f0dadd58cf50cc1c","tid":1357784,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:17:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d9a069925c46a6ab3ae296b2ce2f84635b89c1f","tid":1357784,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9d8d15f7cb820ae416ebabfc2feeeaea155e714","tid":1357784,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:25:19.000Z","msg":"有冇年月日可以查返衝國會嗰陣既事？收鳩啲三毛狗皮"},{"pid":"5e318da98769e0578d850a528c982be121eec45a","tid":1357784,"uid":206617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:29:41.000Z","msg":"德國係呢方面真係好屈機<br />\n用事實去回應左中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1b9da07c1e2e1dd05310593e50d243352df7d8","tid":1357784,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d8d15f7cb820ae416ebabfc2feeeaea155e714","tid":1357784,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:25:19.000Z","msg":"有冇年月日可以查返衝國會嗰陣既事？收鳩啲三毛狗皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.spiegel.de/politik/deutschland/christian-lindner-in-china-fdp-chef-wird-handschlag-verweigert-a-1278378.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Fpolitik%2Fdeutschland%2Fchristian-lindner-in-china-fdp-chef-wird-handschlag-verweigert-a-1278378.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9617605e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spiegel.de/politik/deutschland/christian-lindner-in-china-fdp-chef-wird-handschlag-verweigert-a-1278378.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDen Schilderungen zufolge stellte der Vizeminister die rhetorische Frage, was man in Deutschland mache, wenn Demonstranten in Parlamente wie den Landtag Nordrhein-Westfalens, von wo Lindner stammt, eindr&auml;ngen. Der FDP-Vorsitzende erinnerte daran, dass in Nordrhein-Westfalen tats&auml;chlich einmal Studierende bei Demonstrationen gegen Studiengeb&uuml;hren in das Parlament eingedrungen seien. Gegen diese sei zwar Anzeige erstattet worden, aber gleichzeitig habe sich die Regierungspolitik ver&auml;ndert, weil eine Mehrheit der Gesellschaft mit dem Anliegen sympathisiert habe.<br />\n<br />\n不過都係冇日期或者具體描述，淨係知係喺Nordrhein-Westfalen，應該係Landesparlament地區議會<br />\n求嗰陣既新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e787638263e38933e7df12548a993606e6517a7","tid":1357784,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台仰 東昇<br />\n我知佢地都努力緊"},{"pid":"73fee23066f5ed3f64883b0eb647c4c2b08ffab4","tid":1357784,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.spiegel.de/lebenundlernen/uni/studenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Flebenundlernen%2Funi%2Fstudenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=dc1e0bea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spiegel.de/lebenundlernen/uni/studenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.spiegel.de/lebenundlernen/uni/studenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Flebenundlernen%2Funi%2Fstudenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=dc1e0bea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spiegel.de/lebenundlernen/uni/studenten-belagerten-nrw-landtag-rueckmeldegebuehren-sind-offenbar-vom-tisch-a-201377.html</a><br />\n搵到，好似係，2002年既事，當時NRW政府想將first degree學費加到50 Euro，second degree或者超齡學生就650 Euro<br />\n2000人個德國學生未有申請之下喺D&uuml;sseldorf遊行去議會，當時議會討論緊有關學費既事，跟住啲學生就開始衝擊議會，衝破防線去到議會門口，搞到啲議員入唔到去，最後差佬用馬(?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係我解讀錯)嚟驅趕示威者，最後拉咗21個人，但應該冇到衝入去"},{"pid":"d6e456e785f4429ec642d3bbbe5f4ab78f7b20f6","tid":1357784,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:00:30.000Z","msg":"全球抗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6f8c3b7cdfeb8cb9f48f52b0c9e86b1ddb0105","tid":1357784,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:33:55.000Z","msg":"大巴車落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8f0cfefd06da7856f79e6d50f6ed6a95e654a6","tid":1357784,"uid":268790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"229bf7f98a35537b9389fa5db0f7784d31f2f22e","tid":1357784,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6090a021eafe71b21fb4aa68efb001d6dd693d0","tid":1357784,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n